A wonderful post coming from your perspective.  Not so great coming from mine.<br>
I have no quarrel with those who chose idealism to hide their cowardice, but I do have contempt for those blaspheme the ones who went.<br>
There will always be opportunist that skirt the edge of society for the benefits..but when &quot;their&quot; society moves in a direction that threatens their individual comforts, they quickly fall to the rear until the threat is quelled by others who are unselfish and willing to die for the safety and security of their nation.<br>
Idealism is the beautiful source of positive prophecies, but realism sets the standard for those who survives and those who don't.<br><br>
I am Tatekohomni Wambli and I do not fear the enemy!
